reviewText:
I love the Swedish version
Better

Excellent service by the distributor.

Absolutely excellent example of Nordic Noir and the Wallander series, whether one is a fan of the English language Wallander series or the Swedish language Wallander series---do try both---you will not be disappointed!

absolutely love this series and especially krister henriksson as wallander.  great scripts, locations, acting, direction.  it all comes together to make for a superb series and experience.  highly recommend.
